nd%20shares%204%20trades%20for%20the%20upcoming%20dip%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22stock%20market%20crash%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660425f316bde8d4ead28d05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Eekapol%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDon't%20relax%20just%20yet%20%E2%80%94%20a%20strategist%20who%20predicted%20the%20recent%20pullback%20says%20another%20one%20is%20coming.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELPL's%20Jeffrey%20Buchbinder%20believes%20that%20the%20market%20could%20see%20a%20double-digit%20decline%20in%20September.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20recommends%20buying%20four%20areas%20of%20the%20market%20when%20the%20dip%20comes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20might%20think%20it's%20finally%20time%20to%20take%20a%20breather%20after%20the%20stock%20market%20clawed%20back%20its%20recent%208.5%25%20loss%20over%20the%20last%20few%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Jeffrey%20Buchbinder%2C%20LPL%20Financial's%20chief%20equity%20strategist%2C%20says%20not%20so%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20July%2C%20Buchbinder%20sensed%20that%20the%20market%20was%20ripe%20for%20a%20correction%2C%20writing%20in%20a%20note%20that%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-pullback-overdue-buy-the-dip-investing-strategy-lpl-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20pullback%20is%20overdue%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20predicting%20that%20a%20dip%20would%20emerge%20in%20August.%20After%20disappointing%20July%20jobs%20and%20ISM%20manufacturing%20reports%2C%20the%20market%20swung%20downwards%2C%20extending%20a%20sell-off%20that%20started%20in%20late%20July%20after%20the%20Bank%20of%20Japan%20unexpectedly%20hiked%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Buchbinder%20predicts%20that%20another%20pullback%20is%20in%20store%2C%20and%20it%20could%20be%20right%20around%20the%20corner%20%E2%80%94%20as%20early%20as%20September.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20he%20shared%20why%20he%20thinks%20the%20market%20hasn't%20bottomed%20yet%20and%20his%20top%20trades%20for%20when%20it%20comes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc7a6c6b-b9e4-43b7-ac50-34c2ad56d0b6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20September%20correction%20is%20on%20the%20cards%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20signs%20pointing%20to%20an%20imminent%20correction%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%20according%20to%20Buchbinder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20pullbacks%20of%2010%25%20or%20greater%20are%20quite%20standard%2C%20even%20under%20normal%20economic%20circumstances.%20Buchbinder%20dubs%20these%20as%20%26quot%3Bgarden-variety%20corrections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20more%20likely%20than%20not%20that%20we'll%20get%20a%20crunch%2C%26quot%3B%20Buchbinder%20said.%20%26quot%3BEven%20in%20a%20positive%20year%2C%20the%20average%20maximum%20drawdown%20is%2011%25.%20We%20got%208.5%25%20already.%20That's%20unlikely%20to%20be%20the%20worst%20drawdown%20of%202024%20based%20on%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%20election%20coming%20up%20later%20this%20year%2C%20which%20Buchbinder%20believes%20will%20inject%20added%20volatility%20into%20the%20market.%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20historically%20the%20market%20has%20experienced%20downdrafts%20ahead%20of%20elections.%20Heightened%20geopolitical%20uncertainty%20in%20various%20spots%20around%20the%20world%2C%20such%20as%20Europe%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20could%20also%20make%20markets%20skittish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStocks%20also%20tend%20to%20perform%20worse%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbull-market-rally-stocks-yen-carry-trade-fed-rate-cuts-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESeptember%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20general.%20Although%20there%20isn't%20a%20clear%20reason%20why%20this%20month%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20been%20the%20worst%20performer%20for%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20since%201950%2C%20one%20theory%20is%20that%20investors%20like%20to%20rebalance%20their%20portfolios%20before%20the%20end%20of%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeptember%20is%20a%20very%20weak%20month%20seasonally%2C%20so%20these%20next%20three%20weeks%20would%20be%20a%20logical%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Buchbinder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c4a5af81-36e9-4606-ae03-6d9ee7b1e191%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorrection%2C%20but%20no%20recession%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20sounds%20alarming%2C%20don't%20worry%20%E2%80%94%20Buchbinder%20emphasizes%20that%20while%20pullbacks%20happen%2C%20he%20still%20believes%20the%20US%20economy%20is%20on%20a%20bull%20market%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20get%20a%20bear%20market%2C%20which%20would%20mean%20a%2020%25%20decline%2C%20you%20really%20have%20to%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20evidence%20of%20a%20recession%20or%20certainly%20a%20major%20financial%20crisis%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20see%20signs%20of%20either%20of%20those%2C%26quot%3B%20Buchbinder%20said.%20The%20market%20might%20be%20going%20through%20some%20choppiness%2C%20but%20Buchbinder%20believes%20underlying%20market%20fundamentals%20are%20strong%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they're%20improving%20as%20the%20market%20broadens%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuchbinder%20believes%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20will%20end%20the%20year%20near%20its%20current%20level.%20He's%20also%20not%20writing%20off%20the%20possibility%20of%20an%20end-of-year%20market%20surge%3A%20In%20a%20blue-sky%20scenario%2C%20AI%20tailwinds%2C%20continued%20strong%20corporate%20earnings%2C%20and%20a%20post-election%20rally%20could%20boost%20the%20index%20up%20a%20couple%20hundred%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20path%20to%20get%20there%20would%20probably%20still%20be%20bumpy%2C%20and%20again%2C%20it%20would%20probably%20take%20a%20really%20strong%20Q4%20rally%2C%26quot%3B%20Buchbinder%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Brallies%20after%20election