eport%2C%20commissioned%20by%20the%20Kerala%20government%20and%20headed%20by%20retired%20Justice%20K%20Hema%20revealed%20systemic%20harassment%2C%20abuse%2C%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bcriminal%20nexus%26quot%3B%20within%20the%20industry%2C%20triggering%20high-profile%20resignations%20and%20public%20outcry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh-Profile%20Resignations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20public%20release%20of%20the%20Hema%20Committee%20report%20has%20already%20led%20to%20fallout%20within%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry.%20Two%20high-profile%20figures%2C%20director%20Ranjith%20Balakrishnan%20and%20actor%20Siddique%2C%20have%20resigned%20from%20their%20respective%20positions%20amid%20allegations%20of%20misconduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjith%2C%20a%20prominent%20filmmaker%20and%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Kerala%20Chalachitra%20Academy%20resigned%20following%20accusations%20of%20inappropriate%20behaviour%20by%20a%20Bengali%20actress.%20The%20actress%20alleged%20that%20Ranjith%20misbehaved%20with%20her%20during%20a%20film%20shoot%20several%20years%20ago.%20However%2C%20Ranjith%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations%2C%20claiming%20that%20he%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%20victim%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20targeted%20by%20a%20certain%20section%20of%20people%20since%20the%20day%20I%20took%20charge%20as%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Academy.%20I%20need%20to%20prove%20before%20the%20society%20that%20the%20allegations%20are%20untrue.%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20move%20legally%20and%20bring%20out%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20heard%20saying%20in%20an%20audio%20clip%20sent%20to%20a%20television%20channel%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20people%20including%20the%20media%20are%20attacking%20me%20without%20understanding%20the%20truth.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20step%20down%20from%20the%20post%2C%26quot%3B%20Ranjith%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActor%20Siddique%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Association%20of%20Malayalam%20Movie%20Artists%20(AMMA)%2C%20also%20stepped%20down%20following%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20assault%20by%20an%20actress.%20She%20accused%20Siddique%20of%20sexually%20abusing%20her%20during%20a%20film%20discussion%20when%20she%20was%20just%2021%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarious%20members%20of%20AMMA%2C%20including%20vice%20president%20Jayan%20Cherthala%20and%20actor%20Anoop%20Chandran%2C%20have%20supported%20Siddique's%20decision%20to%20step%20down%20arguing%20that%20it%20was%20morally%20and%20ethically%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Hema%20Committee%20Report%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hema%20Committee%20was%20constituted%20by%20the%20Kerala%20government%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20an%20assault%20case%20involving%20an%20actress.%20The%20actress%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20assaulted%20by%20a%20group%20of%20men%20while%20travelling%20in%202017.%20The%20case%20made%20national%20headlines%20when%20actor%20Dileep%2C%20one%20of%20Malayalam%20cinema's%20biggest%20names%2C%20was%20named%20as%20one%20of%20the%20accused.%20Dileep%20was%20arrested%20and%20kept%20in%20custody%20for%20three%20months%20before%20being%20released%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee's%20mandate%20was%20to%20investigate%20the%20working%20conditions%20of%20women%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%20and%20suggest%20measures%20to%20improve%20their%20safety%20and%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee's%20report%2C%20which%20took%20five%20years%20to%20see%20the%20light%20of%20day%2C%20details%20numerous%20instances%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20exploitation%2C%20and%20gender%20discrimination%20faced%20by%20women%20in%20Malayalam%20cinema.%20The%20report%20highlights%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bpower%20nexus%26quot%3B%20within%20the%20industry%2C%20where%20a%20small%20group%20of%20influential%20men%2C%20including%20producers%2C%20directors%2C%20and%20actors%2C%20allegedly%20control%20the%20fate%20of%20women%20professionals.%20Those%20who%20refuse%20to%20comply%20with%20their%20demands%20are%20systematically%20ostracised%20and%20pushed%20out%20of%20the%20industry%2C%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20Fallout%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20the%20report%20has%20prompted%20strong%20reactions%20from%20political%20parties%20and%20public%20figures.%20The%20opposition%20Congress-led%20United%20Democratic%20Front%20(UDF)%20has%20called%20for%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20by%20a%20team%20of%20women%20IPS%20officers%2C%20while%20the%20Kerala%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20(KPCC)%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20have%20demanded%20strict%20action%20against%20those%20implicated%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kerala%20State%20Women's%20Commission%20has%20also%20taken%20up%20the%20issue%2C%20recommending%20the%20establishment%20of%20grievance%20redressal%20committees%20on%20film%20sets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Women%20in%20Cinema%20Collective%20(WCC)%2C%20a%20group%20of%20women%20professionals%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%20has%20welcomed%20the%20release%20of%20the%20Hema%20Committee%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20a%20long%20journey%20for%20us!%20We%20believed%20that%20our%20fight%20for%20justice%20for%20all%20women%20wanting%20a%20dignified%20professional%20space%20in%20the%20film%20industry%20was%20the%20right%20fight.%20Today%20we%20stand%20vindicated.%20The%20publication%20of%20the%20Hema%20Committee%20report%20is%20another%20step%20that%20WCC%20has%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjith's%20resignation%20has%20been%20welcomed%20by%20many%2C%20including%20state%20Cultural%20Affairs%20Minister%20Saji%20Cheriyan%2C%20who%20said%20that%20the%20Left%20government%20in%20Kerala%20has%20always%20supported%20victims%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724573100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fh5bh7uko_mollywood-_625x300_25_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-profile-resignations-political-fallout-whats-going-on-in-mollywood-6413759%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%20is%20grappling%20with%20allegations%20of%20harassment%20and%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20particularly%20against%20women%20professionals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-profile-resignations-political-fallout-whats-going-on-in-mollywood-6413759%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'He's%20a%20greedy%20...%20'%3A%20Eng%20captain's%20big%20comment%20on%20Joe%20Root%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724572624000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112778346%2Cimgsize-49356.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fhes-a-greedy-england-captain-ollie-popes-big-comment-on-joe-root%2Farticleshow%2F112778317.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Joe%20Root%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20with%20a%20composed%20half-century%20during%20a%20tense%20run-chase%2C%20while%20Smith's%20maiden%20Test%20century%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20gave%20England%20a%20significant%20lead%20of%20122%20runs%2C%20which%20was%20instrumental%20in%20their%20win.%20Reflecting%20on%20his%20captaincy%20in%20Ben%20Stokes'%20absence%2C%20Pope%20said%20he%20enjoyed%20the%20experience%20and%20felt%20confident%20in%20reading%20the%20game%20to%20help%20his%20team%20secure%20all%2020%20wickets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fhes-a-greedy-england-captain-o