0key%20decision-making%20body%20within%20the%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2030%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-hezbollah-commander-fuad-shukr-targeted-by-israel-in-beirut-6226900%5C%22%3EFuad%20Shukr%20was%20targeted%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20in%20Beirut.%20Following%20the%20airstrike%2C%20Lebanese%20security%20sources%20reported%20that%20Shukr%20was%20critically%20injured.%20His%20death%20was%20later%20confirmed%20by%20Israeli%20broadcast%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724567280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fvaq4qse8_fuad-shukr-afp_625x300_25_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-was-fuad-shukr-hezbollah-commander-whose-death-sparked-todays-confict-6413101%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lebanon-%20based%20militant%20group%20Hezbollah%20fired%20a%20large%20number%20of%20missiles%20at%20Israel%20on%20Sunday%2C%20retaliating%20for%20the%20assassination%20of%20their%20senior%20commander%20Fuad%20Shukr%20in%20Beirut%20last%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-was-fuad-shukr-hezbollah-commander-whose-death-sparked-todays-confict-6413101%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vijay%E2%80%99s%20GOAT%20crosses%201%20crore%20mark%20in%20USA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724567008000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112776967%2Cimgsize-85262.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fthalpathy-vijays-the-greatest-of-all-time-goat-cross-rs-1-crore-mark-for-its-premiere-shows-in-usa%2Farticleshow%2F112776999.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphot