es-israel-strikes-lebanon-to-prevent-large-scale-hezbollah-attack-as-middle-east-tensions-rise-6412787%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHezbollah%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20%26quot%3Blarge-scale%26quot%3B%20attacks%20on%20Israeli%20territory.%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20fighter%20jets%20have%20been%20deployed%20to%20neutralise%20these%20threats%2C%20focusing%20on%20Hezbollah%20positions%20that%20posed%20an%20immediate%20danger%20to%20Israeli%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20said%20its%20fighter%20jets%20attacked%20thousands%20of%20Hezbollah%20rocket%20launchers%20in%20south%20Lebanon%20that%20were%20aimed%20at%20northern%20and%20central%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApproximately%20100%20IAF%20fighter%20jets%20...%20struck%20and%20destroyed%20thousands%20of%20Hezbollah%20rocket%20launcher%20barrels%20that%20were%20located%20and%20embedded%20in%20southern%20Lebanon%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Israeli%20military%20statement%20read.%20%26quot%3BMost%20of%20these%20launchers%20were%20aimed%20toward%20northern%20Israel%20and%20some%20were%20aimed%20toward%20central%20Israel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20escalation%20comes%20after%20weeks%20of%20growing%20tension%2C%20with%20Hezbollah%20and%20its%20regional%20ally%2C%20Iran%2C%20vowing%20to%20avenge%20the%20assassination%20of%20its%20military%20commander%20Fuad%20Shukr%20last%20month.%20The%20group%20has%20called%20the%20attack%20on%20its%20commander%20as%20a%20direct%20provocation%20and%20an%20act%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-mossad-hezbollah-abraham-alliance-vs-axis-of-resistance-players-in-israel-iran-shadow-war-6259187%5C%22%3EAbraham%20Alliance%20vs%20Axis%20Of%20Resistance%3A%20Who's%20Fighting%20Israel-Iran%20War%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20context%20of%20the%20initial%20response%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Shukr%2C%20Hezbollah%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bbeg