%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhezbollah-announces-large-scale-attack-israel-begins-pre-emptive-strikes-6412664%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lebanon-based%20militant%20group%20Hezbollah%20and%20Israel%20both%20announced%20large-scale%20military%20operations%20against%20each%20other%20today.%20According%20to%20a%20statement%20from%20Hezbollah%2C%20an%20Iran-backed%20group%2C%20%26quot%3Bmore%20than%20320%26quot%3B%20Katyusha%20rocketswere%20launched.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhezbollah-announces-large-scale-attack-israel-begins-pre-emptive-strikes-6412664%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Why%20Regional%20Films%20Dominated%20The%20National%20Film%20Awards%20This%20Year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fkeqjl7d_rishab-shetty_625x300_17_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegional%20films%20dominated%20the%20National%20Film%20Awards%20this%20year.%20The%2070th%20National%20Film%20Awards%20were%20recently%20announced%20to%20recognize%20the%20best%20of%20Indian%20cinema%20from%202022.%20Film%20star%20Rishab%20Shetty%20won%20the%20Best%20Actor%20award%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%20Kannada%20film%C2%A0%3Ci%3EKantara%3C%2Fi%3E.%20The%20movie%20also%20received%20the%20award%20for%20Best%20Popular%20Film%20Providing%20Wholesome%20Entertainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Best%20Actress%20award%20was%20jointly%20given%20to%20Nithya%20Menen%20for%20the%20Tamil%20film%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThiruchitrambalam%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0and%20Mansi%20Parekh%20for%20the%20Gujarati%20film%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Kutch%20Express%3C%2Fi%3E.%20The%20Malayalam%20film%C2%A0%3Ci%3EAattam%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0won%20Best%20Feature%20Film.%20Pavan%20Raj%20Malhotra%20was%20awarded%20Best%20Supporting%20Actor%20for%20the%20Haryanvi%20film%C2%A0%3Ci%3EFouja%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20while%20Neena%20Gupta%20received%20Best%20Supporting%20Actress%20for%20the%20Hindi%20film%C2%A0%3Ci%3EUunchai%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESooraj%20Barjatya%20was%20honored%20with%20Best%20Director%20for%C2%A0%3Ci%3EUunchai%3C%2Fi%3E.%20Arijit%20Singh%20won%20Best%20Male%20Playback%20Singer%20for%20his%20song%20%E2%80%9CKesariya%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Hindi%20film%C2%A0%3Ci%3EBrahmastra%3A%20Part%201%20%E2%80%93%20Shiva%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20and%20Bombay%20Jayashri%20received%20Best%20Female%20Playback%20Singer%20for%20the%20song%20%E2%80%9CChaayum%20Veyil%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Malayalam%20film%C2%A0%3Ci%3ESaudi%20Vellakka%3C%2Fi%3E.%20A.R.%20Rahman%20won%20Best%20Music%20Director%20(Background%20Music)%20for%20the%20Tamil%20film%C2%A0%3Ci%3EPonniyin%20Selvan%3A%20I%3C%2Fi%3E.%C2%A0%3Ci%3EKGF%20Chapter%202%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20starring%20Yash%2C%20won%20Best%20Kannada%20Film%20and%20Best%20Action%20Direction%20(Stunt%20Choreography).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20films%20also%20received%20awards%20in%20other%20categories%2C%20alongside%20other%20notable%20regional%20films%20from%20various%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%2069th%20National%20Film%20Awards%20held%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Best%20Actor%20honor%20went%20to%20Allu%20Arjun%20for%20the%20Telugu%20movie%C2%A0%3Ci%3EPushpa%3A%20The%20Rise%3C%2Fi%3E.%20Alia%20Bhatt%20and%20Kriti%20Sanon%20shared%20the%20Best%20Actress%20award%20for%20their%20Hindi%20films.%20Gujarati%20cinema%20achieved%20a%20milestone%20when%C2%A0%3Ci%3EGandhi%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0won%20the%20Golden%20Lotus%20for%20Best%20Children's%20Film.%C2%A0%3Ci%3EChhello%20Show%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20which%20won%20Best%20Gujarati%20Film%2C%20was%20nominated%20as%20India's%20official%20entry%20for%20the%20Oscars%202023%20and%20was%20shortlisted%20in%20the%20Best%20International%20Feature%20Film%20category%20but%20did%20not%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20actress%20Nithya%20Menen%2C%20winning%20Best%20Actress%20was%20a%20surprise%2C%20as%20her%20role%20as%20Shobana%20in%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThiruchitrambalam%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0was%20not%20typically%20considered%20a%20strong%20candidate%20for%20a%20national%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20never%20done%20the%20kind%20of%20films%20that%20would%20traditionally%20bring%20national%20awards.%20I%20never%20try%20to%20do%20those%20dramatic%20genres.%20I%20was%20not%20really%20expecting%20the%20award%20at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Menen%2C%20who%20has%20acted%20in%20Malayalam%2C%20Tamil%2C%20Kannada%2C%20and%20Telugu%20films.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegional%20Cinema%20Is%20Challenging%20Bollywood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20success%20of%20regional%20films%2C%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20content%20and%20box%20office%20performance%2C%20has%20shown%20that%20regional%20cinema%20is%20not%20only%20thriving%20but%20also%20challenging%20Bollywood.%20Language%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20barrier%20for%20regional%20films%20attracting%20pan-India%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20note%20that%20theatres%20have%20seen%20hits%20across%20languages.%20In%202023%2C%20Marathi%20film%C2%A0%3Ci%3EBaipan%20Bhari%20Deva%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0and%20Punjabi%20movie%C2%A0%3Ci%3ECarry%20on%20Jatta%203%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0performed%20exceptionally%20well%2C%20alongside%20a%20number%20of%20Hollywood%20hits.%20In%202022%2C%20Kannada%20films%20such%20as%C2%A0%3Ci%3EKantara%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ci%3ECharlie%20777%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0attracted%20large%20crowds%20to%20multiplexes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%2C%20the%20share%20of%20box%20office%20collections%20for%20regional%20films%20in%20India's%20total%20box%20office%20collections%20increased%20from%2040.3%25%20in%20the%20June%202023%20quarter%20to%2056.8%25%20in%20the%20June%202024%20quarter.%20Conversely%2C%20the%20share%20of%20Hindi%20films%20dropped%20from%2041.3%25%20to%2035.1%25%20during%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20rise%20of%20OTT%20platforms%2C%20smartphones%2C%20and%20affordable%204G%20internet%2C%20viewers%20now%20have%20access%20to%20content%20in%20all%20languages.%20South%20Indian%20films%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20have%20gained%20prominence%20through%20remakes%20or%20dubbed%20versions.%20Language%20barriers%20are%20being%20overcome%20with%20high-quality%20dubbing%20of%20regional%20films%20and%20web%20series%20into%20major%20Indian%20and%20international%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMenen%20comments%20on%20regional%20cinema%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CRegional%20films%20are%20a%20huge%20part%20of%20the%20country's%20movie%20industry.%20I%20feel%20language%20is%20definitely%20important.%20People%20connect%20to%20languages%20they%20are%20more%20comfortable%20with.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20dubbing%20and%20the%20kind%20of%20content%20being%20produced%2C%20South%20Indian%20commercial%20films%20are%20appreciated%20even%20in%20northern%20India.%20Dubbing%20is%20definitely%20reducing%20the%20barrier.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPan-India%20Appeal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Indian%20films%20like%C2%A0%3Ci%3EBaahubali%201%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ci%3E2%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ci%3EKGF%201%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ci%3E2%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ci%3ESaaho%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ci%3EPushpa%3A%20The%20Rise%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Ci%3ERRR%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0have%20appealed%20to%20audiences%20across%20India%20due%20to%20their%20high-quality%20dubbing%20and%20content.%20Dhanush's%20song%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20This%20Kolaveri%20Di%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20Gujarati%20song%20%E2%80%9CKhalasi%E2%80%9D%20sung%20by%20Aditya%20Gadhvi%20went%20viral%20throughout%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegional%20stars%20like%20Yash%20(%3Cem%3EKGF%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Kannada)%2C%20Prabhas%20(%3Cem%3EBaahubali%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Telugu)%2C%20Allu%20Arjun%20(%3Cem%3EPushpa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Telugu)%2C%20Ram%20Charan%2C%20and%20Junior%20NTR%20(%3Cem%3ERRR%3C%2Fem%3E)%20have%20developed%20large%20fan%20followings%20beyond%20their%20respective%20states.%20They%20have%20become%20trendsetters%20in%20states%20like%20Bihar%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20Gujarat%2C%20with%20fans%20emulating%20their%20styles%20and%20displaying%20their%20photos%20on%20autorickshaws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20regional%20films%2C%20actors%2C%20and%20actresses%20gain%20fame%20and%20box%20office%20success%2C%20many%20are%20working%20across%20different%20film%20industries%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSlowly%2C%20people%20are%20starting%20to%20accept%20films%20in%20different%20languages.%20I%20think%20that's%20a%20really%20good%20trend.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20specifically%20search%20for%20and%20watch%20Malayalam%20films%20because%20they%20have%20good%20stories.%20I've%20always%20worked%20in%20many%20languages%20myself%20and%20know%20how%20it%20feels%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Menen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20in%20the%20domestic%20market%20but%20also%20internationally%2C%20regional%20content%20in%20any%20language%20has%20become%20popular%20on%20platforms%20like%20Netflix%20and%20Prime%20Video.%20For%20example%2C%C2%A0%3Ci%3ERRR%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0received%20global%20acclaim%2C%20and%20its%20song%20%E2%80%9CNaatu%20Naatu%E2%80%9D%20won%20an%20Oscar%20for%20Best%20Original%20Song.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20perspective%20of%20big%20film%20production%20houses%2C%20the%20demand%20and%20supply%20dynamics%20shape%20their%20movie-making%20business.%20With%20evolving%20audience%20preferences%2C%20technology%20advancements%2C%20and%20emerging%20entertainment%20platforms%2C%20people%20now%20have%20more%20options%20than%20ever%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstron