igation%20team%20had%20recorded%20his%20statement.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAkhtar%20Ali%20worked%20in%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20for%2016%20years.%20He%20began%20as%20assistant%20superintendent%20grade%202%2C%20went%20to%20grade%201%2C%20and%20became%20Deputy%20Superintendent.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20Sandeep%20Ghosh%20came%2C%20this%20was%20the%20number%20one%20college%20in%20eastern%20India.%20It%20is%20a%20100-year-old%20college.%20I%20have%20exposed%20a%20lot%20of%20scams.%20The%20first%20scam%20was%20to%20make%20students%20fail.%20They%20used%20to%20extort%20money%20from%20them%2C%20those%20who%20did%20not%20listen%2C%20and%20some%20students%20used%20to%20collect%20this%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Akhtar%20Ali%20alleged.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThey%20used%20to%20make%20junior%20students%20drink%20alcohol%20and%20make%20them%20protest%2C%20whenever%20it%20came%20to%20Sandeep%20Ghosh's%20transfer.%20The%20illegal%20activities%20include%20smuggling%20of%20bodies%2C%20biomedical%20waste%20scam.%20The%20complaints%20went%20to%20the%20higher%20levels%20including%20vigilance%2C%20but%20nothing%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20Akhtar%20Ali%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20key%20suspect%20in%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20case%20of%20the%20junior%20doctor%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Sanjay%20Roy%2C%20a%20civic%20volunteer%2C%20who%20was%20seen%20in%20the%20hospital's%20CCTV%20near%20the%20crime%20scene.%20Sanjay%20Roy%2C%20Sandeep%20Ghosh%20and%20some%20doctors%20whose%20fingerprints%20were%20taken%20from%20the%20seminar%20hall%20-%20where%20the%20body%20was%20found%20-%20have%20been%20made%20to%20undergo%20lie-detector%20tests.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20CCTV%20footage%20shows%20Sanjay%20Roy%20entering%20the%20hospital%20at%201.03%20am%2C%20sources%20said.%20During%20interrogation%2C%20the%20police%20had%20shown%20him%20the%20CCTV%20evidence%2C%20after%20which%20Sanjay%20Roy%20admitted%20to%20the%20crime%2C%20sources%20have%20s