ct%20of%20N%20Convention%2C%20contrary%20to%20existing%20stay%20orders%20and%20court%20cases.%20I%20thought%20it%20fit%20to%20issue%20this%20statement%20to%20place%20on%20record%20certain%20facts%20for%20protecting%20my%20reputation%20and%20to%20indicate%20that%20we%20have%20not%20done%20any%20actions%20in%20violation%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Nagarjuna%20Akkineni%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20land%20is%20a%20patta%20land%2C%20and%20not%20even%20an%20inch%20of%20tank%20plan%20is%20encroached.%20In%20respect%20of%20the%20building%20constructed%20inside%20the%20private%20land%2C%20there%20is%20a%20stay%20order%20granted%20against%20any%20earlier%20illegal%20notice%20for%20demolition%2C%26quot%3B%20Nagarjuna%20Akkineni%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Telangana%20High%20Court's%20interim%20order%20halting%20the%20demolition%20of%20N-Convention%20Centre%2C%20following%20a%20petition%20by%20the%20facility's%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20clearly%2C%20the%20demolition%20was%20carried%20out%20wrongfully%20based%20on%20misinformation.%20No%20notice%20was%20issued%20prior%20to%20carrying%20out%20the%20demolition%20this%20morning.%20As%20a%20law-abiding%20citizen%2C%20if%20the%20court%20before%20which%20the%20matter%20is%20pending%2C%20had%20decided%20against%20me%2C%20I%20would%20have%20carried%20out%20the%20demolition%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20actor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20placing%20this%20on%20record%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20correcting%20any%20public%20misimpression%20about%20wrongful%20constructions%20or%20encroachment%20by%20us.%20We%20would%20be%20seeking%20appropriate%20relief%20from%20the%20court%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20wrong%20actions%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20authorities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPained%20by%20the%20unlawful%20manner%20of%20demolition%20carried%20out%20in%20respect%20of%20N%20Convention%2C%20contrary%20to%20existing%20stay%20orders%20and%20Court%20cases.%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20thought%20it%20fit%20to%20issue%20this%20statement%20to%20place%20on%20record%20certain%20facts%20for%20protecting%20my%20reputation%20and%20to%20indicate%20that%20we%20have%20not%20done%20any...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Nagarjuna%20Akkineni%20(%40iamnagarjuna)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiamnagarjuna%2Fstatus%2F1827242881674850568%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2024%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20HYDRAA%2C%20in%202014%2C%20the%20Hyderabad%20Metropolitan%20Development%20Authority%20(HMDA)%20issued%20a%20notification%20for%20Tammidikunta%20lake%20describing%20its%20buffer%20zones.%20N-Convention%20had%20then%20approached%20the%20high%20court.%20The%20final%20notification%20was%20issued%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20encroachments%20in%20and%20around%20Tammidikunta%20lake%20and%20connecting%20drains%2C%20the%20area%20around%20Madhapur%20have%20been%20facing%20water-logging%20issues%2C%20HYDRAA%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EN-Convention%20on%20its%20website%20says%20it%20is%20managed%20by%20N3%20Enterprises%20and%20jointly%20owned%20by%20Nagarjuna%20Akkineni%20and%20Nalla%20Preetham.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724559600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fprtfm4tg_nagarjuna-n-convention-centre-_625x300_24_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhyderabad-news%2Fwould-have-demolished-n-convention-centre-myself-actor-nagarjuna-slams-hyderabad-civic-bodies-6412817%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actor%20Nagarjuna%20Akkineni%20has%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20authorities%20in%20Hyderabad%20for%20what%20he%20claimed%20was%20%26quot%3Bunlawful%26quot%3B%20demolition%20of%20his%20N-Convention%20Centre%20in%20the%20city's%20Madhapur%20neighbourhood.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%