20wasting%20my%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harpreet%20shares%20candidly%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20selling%20the%20company%20to%20Aon%20Hewitt%20in%202016%2C%20he%20spent%20a%20few%20years%20following%20his%20passion%20of%20mountaineering%20and%20running%20ultra%20marathons.%20However%2C%20while%20doing%20this%2C%20he%20missed%20out%20on%20spending%20precious%20time%20with%20his%20infant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20left%20him%20wondering%20whether%20he%20was%20making%20the%20right%20choices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20spoke%20to%20any%20older%20person%2C%20the%20one%20regret%20they%20had%20was%20not%20spending%20enough%20time%20with%20their%20children.%20They%20always%20said%20that%20they%20never%20realised%20when%20their%20children%20grew%20up.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20have%20a%20similar%20regret%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Harpreet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERealising%20the%20consequences%20of%20his%20actions%2C%20he%20started%20spending%20more%20time%20at%20home%20with%20his%20daughter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20first%20few%20years%20of%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20life%20along%20with%20a%20parent%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20it%2C%20Suman%20Khanna%2C%20counselling%20psychologist%20and%20founder%2C%20Mind%20Unwind%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20says%20that%20this%20is%20when%20they%20start%20understanding%20the%20world%20and%20environment%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20first%20few%20years%20of%20life%2C%20especially%20the%20first%20six%20months%2C%20a%20child%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20ask%20for%20something.%20The%20presence%20of%20a%20parent%20to%20comfort%20them%20makes%20the%20child%20feel%20safe%20and%20creates%20a%20secure%20attachment%20style.%20This%20ensures%20that%20the%20child%20starts%20trusting%20his%20or%20her%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20this%2C%20Harpreet%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CParenting%20is%20not%20about%20the%20child%2C%20it%20is%20about%20the%20parent.%20Having%20a%20child%20gives%20us%20a%20window%20of%20opportunity%20to%20genuinely%20reflect%20and%20change%20ourselves.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Harpreet%20started%20enjoying%20being%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349527%2Fnew-mothers-online-support-groups-postpartum-breastfeeding-formula-sleep-training-parenting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehands-on%20father%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20had%20a%20blast%20with%20his%20daughter.%20He%20would%20take%20her%20to%20the%20park%2C%20the%20swimming%20pool%20and%20just%20enjoyed%20being%20a%20parent.%20This%20allowed%20him%20to%20notice%20how%20other%20children%20interacted%20with%20their%20parents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTake%20an%20example%20of%20a%20swimming%20class.%20Despite%20some%20children%E2%80%99s%20fear%2C%20the%20instructor%20simply%20throws%20the%20child%20in%20the%20water.%20But%20how%20does%20it%20impact%20the%20child%3F%20Does%20this%20adversely%20affect%20them%3F%20Why%20does%20a%20parent%20allow%20this%3F%20I%20had%20so%20many%20questions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20became%20clear%20to%20him%20that%20the%20blueprint%20of%20a%20well-adjusted%20human%20being%20is%20laid%20out%20in%20the%20early%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20six%20to%20eight%20years%20of%20our%20lives%20matter%20the%20most%20as%20the%20first%20%E2%80%98AI%20model%E2%80%99%20of%20our%20brain%20is%20written%20without%20our%20consent.%20Children%20just%20become%20what%20they%20see%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%20emphatically.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20started%20sharing%20his%20understanding%20of%20parenting%20on%20social%20media%20and%20why%20children%20behave%20a%20certain%20way.%20With%20parents