%20hosts%20at%20Medini%20Homestay%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-4-1724335515.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Medini%20Homestay%20is%20an%20attempt%20at%20sustainable%20living%20and%20responsible%20tourism%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-4-1724335515.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-4-1724335515-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-4-1724335515-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-4-1724335515-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-4-1724335515-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362619%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Medini%20Homestay%20is%20an%20attempt%20at%20sustainable%20living%20and%20responsible%20tourism.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20day%2C%20Deka%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332094%2Frajasthan-rubi-pareek-doubles-profit-with-organic-farming-gives-free-training%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enever%20spray%20any%20chemicals%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%20land.%20It%20is%20six%20years%20and%20his%20commitment%20still%20holds%20true.%20But%2C%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20easy%2C%20he%20cautions.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20will%20make%20mistakes%20and%20you%20will%20learn%20from%20them%2C%20and%20even%20then%2C%20you%20might%20not%20get%20it%20right.%20But%20with%20each%20season%2C%20you%20will%20learn%20to%20refine%20your%20techniques%20and%20to%20read%20your%20plants%20and%20understand%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20making%20inferences%20on%20plant%20health%20when%20he%20begins%20spotting%20signs%20of%20disease%20cropping%20up.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20times%20that%20I%20have%20sent%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20plant%20to%20the%20agricultural%20development%20officer%20explaining%20the%20symptoms.%20They%20responded%20saying%20it%20looked%20like%20a%20fungal%20infection%20and%20that%20I%20should%20resort%20to%20a%20particular%20chemical.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20times%20like%20these%2C%20when%20Deka%20responds%20by%20saying%20he%20does%20not%20use%20chemicals%20on%20his%20plants%2C%20the%20line%20remains%20silent%20at%20the%20other%20end.%20This%20journey%20of%20odds%20would%20deter%20him%20you%E2%80%99d%20think.%20But%20it%20only%20makes%20him%20more%20resilient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288219%2Fafter-visiting-drought-prone-villages-23-yo-plants-3-lakh-trees-in-three-years%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E500-plus%20trees%20that%20dot%20the%20landscape%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20Medini%20Homestay%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Indian%20olive%2C%20guava%2C%20mango%2C%20papaya%2C%20and%20banana%20%E2%80%94%20sway%20in%20the%20breeze%2C%20almost%20bowing%20down%20to%20him%20in%20thanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20passion%20project%20made%20of%20bamboo%20and%20wood%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20property%20around%20the%20Medini%20Homestay%20is%20filled%20with%20trees%20%E2%80%94%20glistening%20water%20droplets%20at%20the%20edges%20of%20the%20leaves%20refracting%20the%20light%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20featuring%20the%20entire%20forest%20in%20a%20single%20drop.%20The%20view%20from%20your%20room%20is%20glorious.%20A%20drone%20view%20of%20the%20property%20reveals%20two%20blocks%20of%20construction.%20As%20Meynell%20explains%2C%20these%20are%20the%20family%20block%20and%20the%20guest%20block.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20both%20identical%20and%20each%20has%20four%20rooms.%20The%20maximum%20capacity%20of%20the%20guest%20block%20is%20to%20accommodate%20nine%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-11-1724336150.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Medini%20Homestay%20is%20made%20out%20of%20bamboo%2C%20mud%2C%20wood%20and%20cow%20dung%20along%20with%20a%20small%20percent%20of%20concrete%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-11-1724336150.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-11-1724336150-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-11-1724336150-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-11-1724336150-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-11-1724336150-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362638%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Medini%20Homestay%20is%20made%20out%20of%20bamboo%2C%20mud%2C%20wood%20and%20cow%20dung%20along%20with%20a%20small%20percent%20of%20concrete.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsk%20Deka%20what%20has%20been%20used%20to%20build%20the%20homes%2C%20and%20he%20responds%20%E2%80%9CEverything%20you%20can%20think%20of.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20probing%20reveals%20bamboo%2C%20wood%2C%20straw%2C%20mud%2C%20cow%20dung%2C%20a%20small%20percentage%20of%20concrete%20bricks%2C%20cement%2C%20and%20corrugated%20sheets%20come%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20%E2%80%9Ceverything%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20basis%20of%20choosing%20these%20materials%20is%20dependent%20on%20their%20availability%20and%20also%20the%20practicality%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20while%20every%20person%20with%20a%20sustainable%20bend%20of%20mind%20starts%20out%20wanting%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335976%2Fmumbai-sustainable-home-ecofriendly-mud-architecture-geeli-mitti-ngo-lakhichand-jain%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuild%20a%20home%20using%20only%20mud%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20calculated%20decisions%20need%20to%20be%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20homestay%2C%20the%20furniture%20is%20handmade.%20The%20bamboo%20and%20cane%20pieces%20were%20made%20in%20Nagaland%20while%20the%20curtains%20were%20handwoven%20in%20the%20studio.%20The%20mirrors%20and%20shelves%20were%20made%20by%20local%20artisans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-12-1724336234.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20decor%20and%20furnishings%20at%20the%20Medini%20Homestay%20are%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20local%20artistry%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-12-1724336234.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-12-1724336234-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-12-1724336234-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-