0India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IRIS%20(Initiative%20for%20Research%20and%20Innovation%20in%20STEM)%20National%20Fair%20was%20the%20proverbial%20game%20changer%20for%20these%20young%20innovators.%20After%20enrolling%20for%20the%20same%20in%202022%2C%20they%20were%20challenged%20to%20create%20a%20working%20prototype%20for%20a%20topic%20they%20chose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20no%20limits%20to%20what%20we%20could%20create.%20We%20wanted%20to%20build%20something%20that%20would%20be%20genuinely%20useful%20to%20our%20families.%20Since%20both%20of%20our%20grandmothers%20had%20mobility%20issues%2C%20we%20focused%20on%20developing%20a%20solution%20for%20elders%20like%20them%20to%20help%20prevent%20falls.%20If%20we%20had%20known%20about%20her%20condition%20earlier%2C%20we%20might%20have%20been%20able%20to%20address%20it%20more%20effectively%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Hriday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20experiences%20ignited%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20desire%20to%20create%20a%20device%20that%20could%20offer%20early%20detection%20of%20mobility%20issues%2C%20potentially%20preventing%20severe%20health%20complications%20down%20the%20line.%20Intense%20brainstorming%20sessions%20followed%2C%20where%20wheelchairs%2C%20walking%20sticks%20and%20more%20were%20discussed.%20%E2%80%9CShould%20it%20be%20a%20foldable%20walking%20stick%2C%20a%20single%20cane%3F%E2%80%9D%20they%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20they%20focused%20on%20creating%20a%20stick%20that%20would%20analyse%20falls%20and%20provide%20a%20diagnosis.%20However%2C%20prohibitive%20costs%20forced%20them%20to%20rethink%20their%20approach.%20Since%20most%20seniors%20with%20gait%20issues%20already%20use%20a%20walking%20stick%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20develop%20a%20system%20that%20could%20be%20easily%20attached%20to%20any%20existing%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20product%20is%20a%20circuit%2C%20an%20attachment%20that%20can%20be%20fitted%20onto%20any%20stick%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%2