0during%20the%20rainy%20season.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20ahead%2C%20Angshuman%20hopes%20to%20purchase%20some%20land%20and%20set%20up%20a%20school%20with%20an%20eco-friendly%20campus.%20He%20also%20wishes%20to%20set%20up%20a%20computer%20lab%20and%20library%20for%20the%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20this%20initiative%20and%20the%20children%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20improve%20the%20economy%20of%20the%20village.%20We%20are%20sowing%20the%20seeds%20of%20entrepreneurship%20in%20these%20children%2C%20which%20will%20reach%20the%20community%20and%20improve%20their%20livelihoods%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Angshuman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296463%2Fjharkhand-teacher-sapan-patralekh-teaches-parents-and-grandparents-improves-literacy-rate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschool%20currently%20has%20105%20students%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20kindergarten%20to%20Class%2012%20and%20seven%20teachers.%20It%20costs%20Rs%20300%20per%20child%20per%20month%2C%20which%20is%20Rs%203%2C600%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20support%20a%20child%20by%20donating%20through%20UPI%20on%207001714095%40axl%20or%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccount%20no%3A%2041165791703%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EName%3A%20Gach%20Green%20Hands%20Social%20Welfare%20Trust%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIFSC%3A%20SBIN0018784%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Angshuman%20Thakur%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724075548000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgacher-skul-min-1724074337.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D361924%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Moved%20by%20the%20plight%20of%20students%20displaced%20amidst%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20in%20Murshidabad%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Angshuman%20Thakur%20started%20the%20Anirvana%20Gacher%20Iskul%20in%202021.%20The%20open-air%20school%20focuses%20on%20practical%20learning%2C%20nature%2C%20culture%20and%20entrepreneurship%20for%20these%20first-generational%20learners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F361924%2Fopen-air-tree-school-west-bengal-murshidabad-inspired-by-tagore-santiniketan-anirvana-gacher-iskul-angshuman-thakur%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2269-YO%20Visually%20Impaired%20Man%E2%80%99s%20Old%20Age%20Home%20Helps%20Abandoned%20Seniors%20Find%20Friendship%20%26amp%3B%20Dignity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20story%20is%20a%20very%20long%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%2069-year-old%20Laljibhai%20Prajapati%20warns%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20putting%20me%20off%2C%20this%20disclaimer%20has%20me%20intrigued.%20I%20am%20finally%20about%20to%20discover%20the%20journey%20of%20this%20visually%20impaired%20stalwart%20in%20starting%20a%20trust%20that%20has%20bettered%20the%20lives%20of%20over%20500%20senior%20citizens%20in%20the%20Kachchh%20region%20of%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20inception%2C%20Shri%20Navchetan%20Andhjan%20Mandal%20has%20been%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20disabled%20individuals%20in%20the%20state%2C%20particularly%20for%20abandoned%20visually%20impaired%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335260%2Fshantanu-naidu-startup-the-goodfellows-helps-senior-citizens-connect-with-youth-ratan-tata%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esenior%20citizens%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Left%20to%20fend%20for%20themselves%20by%20their%20families%2C%20these%20elderly%20individuals%20find%20comfort%20in%20Laljibhai%E2%80%99s%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20he%20takes%20great%20pride%20in%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20reveals%2C%20it%20all%20started%20when%20he%20was%2017%20years%20old.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20eyes%20were%20affected%20by%20glaucoma%20and%20I%20lost%20my%20vision.%20It%20was%20almost%20like%20I%20went%20to%20bed%20one%20night%20and%20woke%20up%20blind%20the%20next%20day.%20My%20life%20changed%20completely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrapped%20in%20the%20four%20walls%20of%20his%20home%20with%20only%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20visits%20to%20look%20forward%20to%2C%20Laljibhai%20felt%20he%20was%20stuck%20in%20a%20proverbial%20tunnel%20%E2%80%94%20one%20without%20a%20light%20at%20the%20end.%20Losing%20his%20eyesight%20had%20done%20more%20than%20fluster%20him%3B%20it%20had%20also%20threatened%20to%20put%20a%20stopper%20on%20his%20career%20goals.%20He%20could%20no%20longer%20hope%20to%20study%20at%20the%20universities%20he%20was%20looking%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Bhachau%20(a%20city%20under%20the%20Kachchh%20district)%20native%20admits%20that%20no%20adversity%20could%20make%20education%20take%20a%20backseat.%20%E2%80%9CI%20began%20travelling%20around%20Gujarat%3B%20to%20Baroda%2C%20Jamnagar%20and%20Ahmedabad.%20I%20began%20studying%20at%20the%20colleges%20there%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F324715%2Fmeet-annie-worlds-first-self-learning-braille-device-that-also-acts-as-a-personal-tutor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20learning%20braille%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%20The%20reason%20to%20set%20his%20sights%20beyond%20Kachchh%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20because%20his%20home%20city%20did%20not%20cater%20to%20blind%20persons.%20In%20the%20years%20that%20followed%2C%20Laljibhai%20obtained%20his%20graduation%20degree%20in%20arts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20in%201975%20when%20he%20returned%20to%20his%20home%20city%2C%20it%20was%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20learning.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20met%20so%20many%20blind%20people%20who%20did%20not%20have%20the%20same%20opportunities%20I%20had%20had%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%20This%20thought%20led%20Laljibhai%20to%20formally%20register%20what%20had%20started%20as%20an%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20Shri%20Navchet