is%20construction%20concede%20that%20ventilated%20terracotta%20tiles%20are%20low-maintenance%20materials.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20reducing%20solar%20heat%20gain%2C%20decreasing%20the%20air%20conditioning%20load%2C%20they%20save%20up%20to%2030%20percent%20energy%20costs.%E2%80%9D%20Because%20of%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F56836%2Faluminium-foil-insulation-in-summer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethermal%20insulation%20capabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20terracotta%20tiles%20reduce%20heat%20transfer%20into%20the%20building%2C%20thus%20maintaining%20a%20stable%20indoor%20temperature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMade%20from%20clay%2C%20which%20is%20naturally%20available%20in%20abundance%2C%20terracotta%20has%20a%20low%20carbon%20footprint%20and%20is%20recyclable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ensure%20that%20the%20material%E2%80%99s%20thermal%20insulation%20aligns%20with%20local%20conditions%2C%20architects%20say.%20Sharing%20some%20precautionary%20advice%2C%20they%20say%20that%20terracotta%20adds%20to%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20facade.%20Hence%20structural%20support%20is%20essential.%20They%20also%20pointed%20out%20how%2C%20in%20this%20particular%20design%2C%20adding%20proper%20ventilation%20behind%20the%20cladding%20went%20a%20long%20way%20to%20prevent%20moisture%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20DGU%20glass%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20marker%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F56423%2Fthis-eco-friendly-house-decor-goals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egood%20aesthetics%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20how%20architect%20Vineeta%20Singhania%20Sharma%20of%20Confluence%20%E2%80%94%20an%20architectural%20firm%20founded%20in%201999%20%E2%80%94%20describes%20this%20material.%20It%20formed%20one%20of%20the%20principal%20elements%20in%20the%20design%20of%20the%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Authority%20of%20India%20(FSSAI)%20office%20at%20Indirapuram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPicture%20two%20panes%20of%20glass%20filled%20with%20a%20buffer%20of%20air%20in%20between.%20This%20is%20how%20the%20material%20appears.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20use%20of%20the%20DGU%20(Double%20Glazed%20Unit)%20glass%20in%20the%20office%20space%20optimises%20the%20daylight%2C%20allowing%20natural%20light%20to%20penetrate.%20Sharma%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20%5BDGU%20Glass%5D%20has%20excellent%20thermal%20insulation%20properties%20and%20maintains%20a%20more%20stable%20internal%20temperature%2C%20reducing%20the%20reliance%20on%20heating%20and%20cooling%20systems.%20This%20leads%20to%20significant%20energy%20savings%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331901%2Fcouple-quit-job-to-build-eco-friendly-carbon-negative-home-homestay-in-himachal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20carbon%20footprint%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1723551625.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DGU%20Glass%20forms%20a%20major%20component%20of%20the%20architecture%20at%20the%20FSSAI%20office%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1723551625.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1723551625-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1723551625-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1723551625-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1723551625-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361165%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDGU%20Glass%20forms%20a%20major%20component%20of%20the%20architecture%20at%20the%20FSSAI%20office%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Confluence%20Consultancy%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20insulation%20capacity%20extends%20to%20noise%20too.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20particularly%20beneficial%20in%20urban%20areas%20or%20near%20busy%20roads%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Since%20the%20material%20works%20to%20insulate%20spaces%2C%20the%20climate%20of%20the%20region%20needs%20to%20be%20kept%20in%20mind.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20structural%20considerations%20need%20to%20be%20made%20to%20ensure%20the%20building%20can%20support%20the%20weight%20and%20thickness%20of%20DGU%20glass%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sharma.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Clay%20bricks%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20of%20American%20architect%20Louis%20Kahn%20was%20considered%20edifying%20by%20devotees%20of%20sustainable%20architecture.%20The%20imprints%20of%20his%20design%20philosophies%20are%20in%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20at%20Ahmedabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20acclaimed%20for%20his%20abstract%20constructions%20that%20featured%20vast%20brick%20walls%20and%20geometric%20voids%2C%20and%20his%20ability%20to%20capitalise%20on%20the%20Sun%E2%80%99s%20shadows.%20It%20is%20with%20Kahn%E2%80%99s%20architectural%20mindset%20in%20view%2C%20that%20architects%20Amit%20Khanna%2C%20Ankita%20Misra%2C%20and%20Krishna%20Yadav%20of%20Amit%20Khanna%20Design%20Associates%20(AKDA)%20have%20design