er%20Angelica%20took%20a%20trip%20from%20Chandigarh%20to%20Khardung%20La%20in%202021%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ajay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAngelica%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F54409%2Fall-women-biker-clubs-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenthusiasm%20for%20bike%20rides%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20rooted%20in%20her%20subconscious.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20she%20was%20all%20of%20four%20months%20old%20and%20her%20neck%20was%20stabilised%2C%20I%20would%20tuck%20her%20into%20the%20baby%20carrier%2C%20which%20I%20would%20then%20place%20on%20the%20bike%20tank.%20As%20soon%20as%20I%20began%20riding%2C%20she%E2%80%99d%20fall%20asleep%20within%20seconds%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ajay%20shares.%20Then%20followed%20rides%20to%20school%2C%20trips%20to%20the%20hill%20station%20Nandi%20Hills%20and%20Hampi%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20drives%20to%20Puducherry%20and%20Goa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoad%20trips%20became%20the%20duo%E2%80%99s%20love%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20they%20are%20reeling%20from%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20trip%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20covering%207%2C000%20km%20from%20Kanyakumari%20to%20Thang%20in%20Ladakh%20in%2024%20days.%20In%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethey%20revisit%20the%20past%20few%20years%20and%20the%20travels%20that%20have%20brought%20them%20closer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20lifetime%E2%80%99s%20worth%20of%20lessons%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20being%20stuck%20in%20a%20landslide%20for%20four%20days%2C%20driving%20through%20crumbling%20roads%20and%20being%20deserted%20without%20fuel%2C%20teach%20you%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20makes%20you%20more%20intuitive%2C%20says%20Angelica.%20Like%20her%20teen%20counterparts%2C%20she%20recalls%20being%20%E2%80%9Cfussy%E2%80%9D%20about%20her%20food%20preferences%2C%20luxuries%20and%20comforts.%20Bad%20weather%20wo